column5: If you could win any walleye Tournament in Canada what would it be.Give reason. As well what is the top tournament in Canada.
Mine would be all of them back to back
I can't imagine fishing myself fishing in a tournament.I go fishing to get away from all the competitions we face daily in this world.
You have fish in Canada? Oh ya and your money looks funny too!
Oh, you must be thinking of Canadian Tire Money, its almost as good as the real stuff. (but only in their stores)
